# automation.mcp
# Rules for AI workflows, automations, and validation
# Author: Oli Meimberg
# Version: 1.0

rules:
  - type: custom
    note: >
      AI-assisted development principles:
      - Validate AI-generated code before committing
      - Review security implications of generated code
      - Test thoroughly, especially edge cases
      - Maintain code consistency with project style
      - Document AI-generated complex logic
      - Human review required for critical paths

  - type: custom
    note: >
      Automation guidelines:
      - Automate repetitive tasks
      - Keep automation scripts in version control
      - Document automation workflows
      - Implement proper error handling
      - Log automation activities
      - Make automations idempotent where possible

